28 (27). Head high, height to length ratio nearly 2:1. Eye height to length ratio 2:1. Lunule subequal in height to length to frons, with conspicuous proclinate black setulae. Ocellar seta absent. Anterior ocellus surrounded by ring of short black setulae. Neotropical (predators of eggs within coccoid ovisac)....................... (
